additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: INGREDIENTS: Dark Chocolate (74%) [Cocoa Mass, Sugar, Cocoa Butter, Cocoa Powder, Milk Solids, Emulsifier (322), Natural Flavouring, Macadamia Nut, Almonds, Hazelnut], Dried Cherries (25%) [Cherry, Sugar, Sunflower Oil], Tapioca Starch [Glazing Agent (Tapioca Starch), Sugar], 904 [Glazing Agent (904), Sunflower Oil].

description: A seasonal favourite of dried cherries coated in dark chocolate. Perfect as an evening indulgence or for entertaining.
